uflowchart LR
    %% Target-state system context. Current implementation is backend-first and does not yet include auth, worker, storage, or observability.
    FinanceUser[Finance User] --> WebApp[Web App]
    Reviewer[Reviewer] --> WebApp
    Admin[Admin] --> WebApp
    Auditor[Auditor] --> WebApp

    WebApp --> API[FastAPI Backend]

    API --> Auth[Authentication and RBAC]
    API --> Database[(PostgreSQL)]
    API --> Cache[(Redis)]
    API --> ObjectStorage[(Private Object Storage)]
    API --> Queue[Invoice Processing Queue]

    Queue --> Worker[Background Worker]
    Worker --> OpenAI[OpenAI API]
    Worker --> Database
    Worker --> ObjectStorage
    Worker --> VectorStore[(pgvector)]

    API --> Observability[Logs Metrics Traces]
    Worker --> Observability
    Observability --> Dashboards[Grafana Dashboards]
